description: Spectacular 2022 ground-up new construction, 4-bed, 3.5 bath single family with garage parking & 3 private decks on desirable East Side.This thoughtfully designed home has a fantastic floor plan highlighted by sprawling living space, high ceilings & show-stopping floor-to-ceiling windows. The expansive open concept living space feat. a high-end kitchen with Miele appliances, quartz counters, separate custom wet bar/wine fridge & opens onto a deck, perfect for entertaining or for your morning cup of coffee. The kitchen flows into the living/dining room that is flooded with light from its south-facing exposure. Upstairs are 2 huge guest bedrooms, full bath, laundry & a deck. Top floor is fully encompassed by the primary suite with a private deck, walk-in closet, luxurious bath with a separate water closet, soaking tub & W/D. Fabulous bonus room with a full bath on the lower level is perfect for a den/guest room/office. Highlights incl: motorized blinds, surround sound & garage parking.
